Healthcare Solutions revenue growth to be in the range of 7 to 8 percent, narrowed from the previous range of 6 to
8 percent;
International Healthcare Solutions revenue to be in the range of a 3 percent decline to flat, up from the previous range
of a 1 to 5 percent decline;
Adjusted Diluted Earnings Per Share to be in the range of $11.70 to $11.90, representing growth of 6 to 8 percent, raised from
the previous range of $11.50 to $11.75;
On a constant currency basis, adjusted diluted earnings per share growth to be in the range of 8 to 10 percent, raised
from the previous range of 6 to 9 percent;
Excluding contributions related to COVID-19, adjusted diluted earnings per share growth to be in the range of 11 to 13
percent, raised from the previous range of 9 to 11 percent; and
On a constant currency basis excluding contributions related to COVID-19, adjusted diluted earnings per share
growth to be in the range of 13 to 15 percent, raised from the previous range of 11 to 13 percent.

